\u270\'0eakujem. Tie\u382\'7e m\u225\'e1m kontakty so \u353\'61tudentmi vysok\u253\'fdch \u353\'61k\u244\'f4l, a u\u382\'7e dlhoro\u269\'0dn\u233\'e9, a m\u244\'f4\u382\'7eem v\u225\'e1m poveda\u357\'65, \u382\'7ee keby som dala ich n\u225\'e1zory dohromady, tak tu odcitujem opa\u269\'0dn\u253\'fd n\u225\'e1zor s viacer\u253\'fdmi podpismi. A ke\u271\'0f ste tu pre\u269\'0d\u237\'edtali to, \u269\'0do ste \u269\'0d\u237\'edtali, ste ma presved\u269\'0dili e\u353\'61te viac o tom, \u382\'7ee mus\u237\'edm hlasova\u357\'65 za predlo\u382\'7een\u253\'fd legislat\u237\'edvny n\u225\'e1vrh.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
A k v\u225\'e1\u353\'61mu n\u225\'e1zoru, \u382\'7ee v z\u225\'e1konoch ma\u357\'65 niektor\u233\'e9 ustanovenia je kontraprodukt\u237\'edvne. P\u225\'e1n poslanec, ako zd\u244\'f4vodn\u237\'edte, \u382\'7ee v zahrani\u269\'0d\u237\'ed v z\u225\'e1konoch, u\u382\'7e som to tu povedala, nie v jednom, s\u250\'fa tak\u233\'e9to ustanovenia, \u382\'7ee mus\u237\'ed ovl\u225\'e1da\u357\'65 \u353\'61t\u225\'e1tny jazyk pracovn\u237\'edk \u353\'61t\u225\'e1tnej spr\u225\'e1vy, \u382\'7ee mus\u237\'ed sklada\u357\'65 s\u318\'3eub a podobne. Pre\u269\'0do to maj\u250\'fa, ke\u271\'0f je to kontraprodukt\u237\'edvne? \u268\'0co chc\u250\'fa potrie\u357\'65 oni svoje vlastenectvo, ke\u271\'0f maj\u250\'fa tak\u233\'e9to ustanovenia? \u268\'0co n\u225\'e1m to tu rozpr\u225\'e1vate?! }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
Ja skuto\u269\'0dne nie som absol\u250\'fatny nevedomec o z\u225\'e1konoch v zahrani\u269\'0d\u237\'ed a m\u244\'f4\u382\'7eem v\u225\'e1m poveda\u357\'65, tak\u233\'e9to ustanovenia maj\u250\'fa, aplikuj\u250\'fa a dodr\u382\'7eiavaj\u250\'fa. Nielen\u382\'7ee ich maj\u250\'fa v platnom pr\u225\'e1ve, ale ich aplikuj\u250\'fa a dodr\u382\'7eiavaj\u250\'fa. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
\u268\'0ci\u382\'7ee m\u328\'48a ste pr\u225\'e1ve svoj\u237\'edm vyst\u250\'fapen\u237\'edm presved\u269\'0dili o opaku, \u269\'0do ste tu hovorili, a je mi smutn\u233\'e9, \u382\'7ee bud\u250\'faci u\u269\'0ditelia maj\u250\'fa tak\u253\'fdto postoj, ktor\u237\'ed n\u225\'e1m bud\u250\'fa vychov\u225\'e1va\u357\'65 deti, \u271\'0fal\u353\'61iu gener\u225\'e1ciu, alebo bud\u250\'fa v\u253\'fdchovu ovplyv\u328\'48ova\u357\'65. }
