\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6

\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\b\afs30\ab\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
M. Bel\u225\'e1sov\u225\'e1, poslanky\u328\'48a: }{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
\u270\'0eakujem za slovo. P\u225\'e1n poslanec Abrhan, vyjadr\u237\'edm sa k tomu \u250\'fa\u269\'0delov\u233\'e9mu, nazvem to \u250\'fa\u269\'0delov\u233\'e9mu, vyhl\u225\'e1seniu \u353\'61tudentov Filozofickej fakulty. Vypichnem niektor\u233\'e9 fr\u225\'e1zy z neho: \u8222\'1enemali by sme prekr\u250\'faca\u357\'65 fakty\u8220\'1c, \u8222\'1emali by sme bra\u357\'65 oh\u318\'3ead na druh\u233\'e9 \u353\'61t\u225\'e1ty, n\u225\'e1rody\u8220\'1c. No, toto s\u250\'fa argumenty, ktor\u233\'e9 sme po\u269\'0d\u250\'favali za komunizmu. Za komunistov. Vtedy, ke\u271\'0f sme len n\u225\'e1znakom spomenuli nie\u269\'0do vlasteneck\u233\'e9 alebo sme sa len op\u253\'fdtali, tak sme boli bur\u382\'7eo\u225\'e1zni nacionalisti. A mysl\u237\'edm si, \u382\'7ee tieto n\u225\'e1zory, ktor\u233\'e9 boli vtedy v podstate takou \u353\'61t\u225\'e1tnou politikou, pretrv\u225\'e1vaj\u250\'fa dodnes. Dodnes. Mo\u382\'7eno je to aj t\u253\'fdm, \u382\'7ee t\u237\'ed historici mnoh\u237\'ed z tej totality s\u250\'fa zamontovan\u237\'ed e\u353\'61te aj do dne\u353\'61n\u253\'fdch, realiz\u225\'e1cie dne\u353\'61nej hist\u243\'f3rie, v\u253\'fdkladu hist\u243\'f3rie a dej\u237\'edn. T\u253\'fdm nechcem poveda\u357\'65, \u382\'7ee t\u237\'edto \u353\'61tudenti s\u250\'fa komunisti, len st\u225\'e1le v podstate s\u250\'fa ovplyv\u328\'48ovan\u237\'ed t\u253\'fdmito n\u225\'e1zormi.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
Ja si nemysl\u237\'edm, \u382\'7ee by sme sa mali pri v\u253\'fdklade svojich dej\u237\'edn d\u237\'edva\u357\'65 na druh\u233\'e9 \u353\'61t\u225\'e1ty, aby sme, nech Boh chr\u225\'e1ni, ich neurazili, tie ostatn\u233\'e9 \u353\'61t\u225\'e1ty a n\u225\'e1rody. Nikto to takto nerob\u237\'ed. Ve\u271\'0f my najlep\u353\'61ie vieme, ak\u233\'e9 boli na\u353\'61e dejiny. My najlep\u353\'61ie vieme preto, lebo sme ich pre\u382\'7eili. M\u225\'e1me s t\u253\'fdm sk\u250\'fasenosti. Tak\u382\'7ee ke\u271\'0f my p\u237\'ed\u353\'61eme o svojich dejin\u225\'e1ch a m\u225\'e1me svoj v\u253\'fdklad vlastenectva a dej\u237\'edn a hist\u243\'f3rie, tak je to autentick\u233\'e9. A mali by sme sa presta\u357\'65 d\u237\'edva\u357\'65 na to, \u269\'0do povedia, nedajbo\u382\'7ee, in\u233\'e9 n\u225\'e1rody. Lebo toto je potom na\u353\'61a z\u225\'e1huba a na\u353\'61a trag\u233\'e9dia.}
